text:
Will we really have to send our users through a third party redirect to have a HubSpot link open in a new tab?
As far as I am aware, we don’t have access to `window` and we can’t specify target.
It would be great with a `target` property to set `current`, `newTab`, etc.

<@U06RECNLTEJ> do you happen to have the version of your extension in the "before state" that had the bug? We'd love to test it out if so. We expect most things to "just work" so I want to make sure we're not missing anything
I miss the builder too, almost every day. Heard. :ear:
